    conversion helper script with some hand touch-ups.
  * Used <sect> for any level for the ease of reorganizing generated XML text
    for debiandoc2xml.
  * Fixed DTD header for XML output. (closes: #430576)
  * Added Wiki snippet generation capability. (closes: #396839)
  * Fixed example output bug for XML. (closes: #431126)
  * Updated README.Debian so people will read debiandoc-sgml-doc before doing
    XML conversion and recommend DocBook XML usage. (closes: #431170)

