    in environment variables locale settings if '-l' option is not used
  * Format/HTML.pm: fixed locale to language tag conversion
  * Locale: proper introduction of support for Euro-based locales
  * Locale/zh*: fixed translation errors
    (closes: Bug#231990)
  * Format/LaTeX.pm: added hyperref driver based on output format
    (partial fix for Bug#214249)
