  * Moved the code readiing the i18n data to the common module and made
    fail gracefully (fixing bugs #35934 and #37268) (thanks Adam!)
  * Restructured the i18n data directory structure mimicing the structure
    under /usr/share/locale to support languages with more than one country
    and/or more than one character encodings
  * i18n/*: added missing i18n data (fixing somewhat more of bug #31266
    and also fixing bug #36238) (thanks Marcelo!)

