debiandoc-sgml (1.1.19) unstable; urgency=low

  * debiandoc2*: added missing ':' after 'p' in options for `getopt`
    (fixing bug #35517) (thanks Adam!)
  * Reorganized i18n data directory structure: Now adding a new language
    doesn't require a code change anymore (unless it needs new special
    functionality)
  * Completed i18n data structure with all missing strings (now we only
    need the missing proper translations) (fixing half of bug #31266)
  * Added Czech i18n support (thanks Jiri!)
  * Added initial ISO 8859-5 Russian support (thanks Peter!)
    (Michael: KOI8-R will follow, but requires some more work)
  * spec/texinfo: initial i18n support
  * spec/*: code clean-up of and more idiom in format modules

